{"tid":1838094,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[彩你有味] 廣東湖北田鼠孔雀照有售","createTime":"2020-01-24T01:50:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T02:18:41.000Z","uid":1886,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"dfd960e9a7172ee9e19d0131a5e86a158667b4f4","tid":1838094,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T01:50:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200124/L3PCNEJN7SVYV2VC4NCUG5Z6EM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200124%2FL3PCNEJN7SVYV2VC4NCUG5Z6EM%2F&d=J5HXnbFloTEqGlUzWM3JX13VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=951ee027\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200124%2FL3PCNEJN7SVYV2VC4NCUG5Z6EM%2F&h=69ce110e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200124/L3PCNEJN7SVYV2VC4NCUG5Z6EM/</a><br />\n<br />\n在相距武漢不到1,000公里的廣東依然「冇有怕」，「背脊向天，人皆可食」，深信以形補形之道，讓地下野味市場有價有市，屢禁不止。記者近期兩度走訪廣州一帶，在當地司機帶路下，在天河區邊陲找到一間隱蔽的野味餐廳，從廣州南站出發，車程近1個小時。司機笑指：「如果冇熟人帶路，唔好話你，我都唔知點搵。」飯店置身農家老房子之中，頗為殘破，廚房開揚，但骯髒不堪，載着肉料碎屑的盤子胡亂擺放，也有老鼠在場「搵食」。<br />\n<br />\n記者表明替老闆找野味後，店方人員拉開飯店前門儲物倉的鐵閘，讓記者先「睇貨」。儲物倉大概十餘個小鐵籠，分別困住3、4隻田鼠和竹鼠、10多條眼鏡蛇，還有水魚、鱷龜各一。該男子向記者稱「野的」，隨後便匆匆關閘，另外一名廚房阿姐向記者推介孔雀：「1,000元人民幣（下同，1,125港元）一隻，可以打火鍋。」記者當時稱明天帶老闆來這裏用膳，並乘的士離開。<br />\n<br />\n在向來以食野味而聞名的從化區，在當地的新城市場及西城市場找到水律蛇、斑鳩等野味。老闆娘稱：「水律蛇130蚊（146港元）一斤，一條收你400蚊（450港元），之前捉咗幾條返嚟，好多客人要，宜家得返一條，你要嘅話我就劏，斑鳩40元（45港元）一隻。」記者佯稱要再看看價錢後離去。"},{"pid":"bb1dc3592f56111a7f5177570b69196389cc4826","tid":1838094,"uid":83251,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T01:51:08.000Z","msg":"彩你有味食野味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c373ec691eaabf797ad449d81299fe2def380a53","tid":1838094,"uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T01:51:10.000Z","msg":"而即使武漢肺炎傳至廣東，仍無人戴口罩，甚至連從化區中醫醫院也沒有多少個人戴口罩，更別奢望區內有多少防疫措施。當地一間士多老闆娘自信滿滿地向記者稱：「深圳嗰邊有咋嘛，邊有咁易中呀！」"},{"pid":"2dd3b5582bb1282a6b72e1581be3b108ed910653","tid":1838094,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb1dc3592f56111a7f5177570b69196389cc4826","tid":1838094,"uid":83251,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T01:51:08.000Z","msg":"彩你有味食野味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T01:52:29.000Z","msg":"【第廿叄期牆紙x民記】黃色經濟起革命 良心消費衛我城<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1833670/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1833670/page/1</a><br />\nFB : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/852wallpaper/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F852wallpaper%2F&d=J5HXnbFloTEqGlUzWM3JX13VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=e910b646\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/852wallpaper/</a><br />\nTG : <a href=\"https://t.me/WallPaperENews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWallPaperENews&d=J5HXnbFloTEqGlUzWM3JX13VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=2d62b539\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/WallPaperENews</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pyqDTS2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpyqDTS2.jpg&h=6706d986&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9a33fbc738382bf0fe59702bdbd4048889ff2bc9","tid":1838094,"uid":8880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T01:52:54.000Z","msg":"支持繼續食野味 相信黨的力量 什麼鬼肺炎是造謠"},{"pid":"749b02de1d989705d903f8f0fc5133839aa30092","tid":1838094,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb1dc3592f56111a7f5177570b69196389cc4826","tid":1838094,"uid":83251,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T01:51:08.000Z","msg":"彩你有味食野味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif